title: AHS 1984 - Full Cast Announcement Promo
author: AHS Leaks
comment: I was just happy to see Emma. It seems they might be actually giving her freedom to play a non bitchy role. I hope so. I enjoyed her Freakshow character. Madison is a forever favorite but I also like her.
Love seeing the Scream Queens people showing up in this, just wish they'd get Glen Powell, he's so freaking perfect for that stereotypical "preppy guy" from the 80's.
I'm unsure if this is just how Ryan Murphy holds auditions or just a really awkward and cringy reel.
So is it a show or a Tyler the creator fashion video?
